WEBVTT

01:58.640 --> 02:01.230
This wound was inflicted by Liu Chu.

02:01.950 --> 02:03.480
If I don't destroy Jinglan,

02:03.680 --> 02:05.740
then I am not worthy to be called a man.

02:07.640 --> 02:08.570
You must help me.

02:09.910 --> 02:11.840
Help me wipe out this humiliation.

02:12.310 --> 02:13.680
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

02:13.680 --> 02:15.000
I will do my best.

02:15.960 --> 02:18.280
If we cannot secure
a swift victory on the battlefield,

02:18.280 --> 02:20.540
then we will tear them apart from within.

02:26.680 --> 02:27.470
Good.

02:28.240 --> 02:29.030
Good.

02:30.520 --> 02:31.430
Oh.

02:31.560 --> 02:32.890
You've done much for me.

02:33.750 --> 02:34.560
Rest assured.

02:35.680 --> 02:37.310
When Jinglan falls,

02:37.560 --> 02:38.360
that will be

02:38.680 --> 02:40.710
the day I name you my queen.

02:44.680 --> 02:46.750
As long as I can stay by your side,

02:48.120 --> 02:49.750
I will be content.

02:50.079 --> 02:51.240
Father.

02:54.520 --> 02:55.680
Lord Meng.

02:56.910 --> 02:58.520
I have other matters to handle.

02:58.520 --> 02:59.910
Stay here and keep your father company.

02:59.910 --> 03:00.750
Okay.

03:01.520 --> 03:02.520
Greetings, Fa...

03:04.360 --> 03:05.620
Father, your wound...

03:06.120 --> 03:06.870
What?

03:07.800 --> 03:09.150
Is this how you bow to me?

03:09.710 --> 03:12.370
Is that what
the ceremonial officer taught you?

03:14.960 --> 03:16.150
Greetings, Father.

03:16.400 --> 03:17.000
Hmm.

03:17.430 --> 03:18.560
That's more like it.

03:23.520 --> 03:24.280
Father.

03:24.630 --> 03:26.150
Since I was a child, you had me taught

03:26.150 --> 03:27.030
virtue, humility,

03:27.030 --> 03:28.240
and all the rules of court etiquette.

03:28.240 --> 03:29.910
But what use are any of those?

03:30.030 --> 03:31.710
In Changmo, besides you,

03:31.710 --> 03:34.110
who else deserves
such a formal bow from me?

03:34.360 --> 03:36.520
Even if you do not bow to me,

03:37.079 --> 03:39.910
you must bow
to your husband in the future.

03:39.910 --> 03:41.000
Liu Chu?

03:41.120 --> 03:41.630
Yes.

03:43.520 --> 03:45.030
Ever since I was young,
you've told me that

03:45.030 --> 03:46.750
one day I would marry

03:46.750 --> 03:48.560
Liu Chu, the prince of Jinglan.

03:49.310 --> 03:50.840
But I've never even met him.

03:51.150 --> 03:53.960
Even though you've never met,

03:54.360 --> 03:57.030
he already loves you deeply.

03:57.190 --> 03:58.120
He loves me?

03:58.910 --> 04:00.240
How much does he love me?

04:00.360 --> 04:02.150
Well, let me put it this way.

04:03.080 --> 04:04.910
He is your destined one.

04:05.560 --> 04:06.840
In the near future,

04:06.870 --> 04:09.730
he will bring you back
to Jinglan in a grand wedding,

04:10.030 --> 04:12.160
and make you his most beloved consort.

04:12.470 --> 04:14.120
You will have many children,

04:14.520 --> 04:16.630
and spend your life in happiness

04:16.680 --> 04:18.279
within his splendid palace.

04:18.720 --> 04:20.430
Who would want to have children with him?

04:20.430 --> 04:22.480
I want to stay with you forever.

04:24.600 --> 04:25.950
You silly girl.

04:26.480 --> 04:27.720
By then,

04:27.750 --> 04:30.950
Jinglan and Changmo will be one family.

04:31.160 --> 04:34.510
We can invite Liu Chu to Changmo.

04:34.750 --> 04:35.800
That way,

04:35.800 --> 04:37.130
you can stay with Liu Chu

04:37.310 --> 04:38.720
and also stay with me.

04:39.270 --> 04:40.070
How about that?

04:40.070 --> 04:40.680
Good.

04:46.070 --> 04:47.360
Thank you, Father.

04:48.310 --> 04:49.360
I believe

04:49.360 --> 04:51.390
Liu Chu and I will be happy together.

04:51.830 --> 04:53.480
I also hope there will never be war

04:53.480 --> 04:55.310
between our two nations again.

05:05.240 --> 05:06.040
Princess.

05:06.070 --> 05:07.830
Lord Fei, General Xiao.

05:08.270 --> 05:09.510
Princess, you haven't
entered the palace yet,

05:09.510 --> 05:11.510
so the daily greetings
are still necessary.

05:11.510 --> 05:12.510
What greetings?

05:12.950 --> 05:14.350
It's just surveillance.

05:14.430 --> 05:15.950
The princess holds a noble status.

05:15.950 --> 05:18.040
We just want to ensure her safety.

05:18.680 --> 05:20.240
Lord Fei, thank you.

05:20.920 --> 05:21.360
It's nothing.

05:21.360 --> 05:23.560
So you know we are here
for a marriage alliance.

05:23.560 --> 05:24.750
Then when will your Emperor come

05:24.750 --> 05:26.210
to take the princess back?

05:26.430 --> 05:28.360
A marriage alliance is a matter
of great importance.

05:28.360 --> 05:29.510
It is complex and requires
careful preparation.

05:29.510 --> 05:31.310
Everything must be properly arranged.

05:31.310 --> 05:31.950
Princess,

05:32.159 --> 05:32.830
please believe that His Majesty

05:32.830 --> 05:35.360
will prepare a grand ceremony for you.

05:37.360 --> 05:39.480
Jin Xi, since we've arrived
in the capital,

05:39.480 --> 05:40.750
there's no need to rush.

05:40.750 --> 05:43.409
I believe His Majesty
has his own arrangements.

05:43.510 --> 05:44.950
We shall follow General Xiao's lead.

05:44.950 --> 05:46.560
Thank you for
your understanding, Princess.

05:46.560 --> 05:48.560
Then I will take my leave first.

05:54.630 --> 05:56.230
If you feel bored, Princess,

05:56.240 --> 05:58.240
you are free to walk around the courtyard.

05:58.240 --> 05:59.440
If you need anything,

05:59.510 --> 06:00.950
you can also ask General Chengfeng

06:00.950 --> 06:01.880
to buy it for you.

06:01.950 --> 06:02.480
All right.

06:02.480 --> 06:03.000
Then,

06:03.310 --> 06:05.240
I will take my leave as well.

06:14.430 --> 06:16.560
Jin Xi, don't worry.

06:16.830 --> 06:18.160
I trust Father's words.

06:18.720 --> 06:19.920
Liu Chu will surely be

06:20.310 --> 06:22.560
a husband who loves me deeply.

06:26.240 --> 06:27.240
This wine is good.

06:27.830 --> 06:28.630
Have a taste.

06:30.360 --> 06:31.560
I still have official matters
to attend to later,

06:31.560 --> 06:32.560
so I won't drink.

06:34.310 --> 06:35.360
You and Xiao Chi—

06:35.750 --> 06:36.950
one refuses to drink,

06:37.360 --> 06:39.420
the other doesn't even show up at all.

06:39.560 --> 06:41.560
Your Majesty,
you suddenly have the mood for drinking—

06:41.560 --> 06:43.220
has something good happened?

06:43.720 --> 06:44.600
Yesterday,

06:44.870 --> 06:47.680
Lord Li brought Wang Ruhai
to me to plead for mercy.

06:47.680 --> 06:48.480
I refused.

06:48.560 --> 06:49.510
Is that so?

06:49.920 --> 06:51.560
You should have seen it.

06:51.750 --> 06:53.000
He knelt under the blazing sun

06:53.000 --> 06:54.430
for two whole hours.

06:54.510 --> 06:56.430
He was limping when he got up to leave.

06:56.430 --> 06:57.830
It was quite satisfying.

06:59.360 --> 07:00.190
Well.

07:00.630 --> 07:02.430
Wang Ruhai got what he deserved.

07:02.950 --> 07:05.480
What a pity I didn't get to
see his sorry state.

07:05.680 --> 07:06.430
Ah.

07:07.390 --> 07:08.160
Ah.

07:08.430 --> 07:09.190
Damn it.

07:09.510 --> 07:09.950
I...

07:10.680 --> 07:11.120
I...

07:11.560 --> 07:12.360
I'm really...

07:14.360 --> 07:16.360
furious.

07:18.720 --> 07:20.430
His Majesty.

07:21.310 --> 07:21.830
Humph.

07:22.270 --> 07:22.870
No.

07:23.120 --> 07:26.360
Liu Chu, Xiao Chi and Fei Zheng,

07:26.680 --> 07:28.360
just you wait.

07:28.920 --> 07:30.270
All of you—

07:30.430 --> 07:31.560
just wait!

07:32.120 --> 07:32.950
By the way,

07:33.950 --> 07:35.159
when do you plan

07:35.630 --> 07:37.960
to set the date for the marriage alliance?

07:38.680 --> 07:41.120
We can take our time with this.

07:41.120 --> 07:42.510
I'm not in a hurry anyway.

07:42.510 --> 07:44.560
Aren't you curious

07:44.560 --> 07:46.620
what the Princess of Changmo is like?

07:46.830 --> 07:48.310
If

07:48.920 --> 07:51.720
I see an ugly woman

07:52.430 --> 07:53.890
at the marriage ceremony,

07:53.950 --> 07:54.950
can I back out?

07:56.560 --> 07:57.950
Of course you can't.

07:58.920 --> 07:59.870
So, Your Majesty...

07:59.870 --> 08:01.680
don't you want to

08:01.750 --> 08:03.750
see her yourself?

08:04.630 --> 08:06.830
You really know how to keep me guessing.

08:08.120 --> 08:09.680
But I'm not falling for it.

08:09.950 --> 08:11.070
Well.

08:11.070 --> 08:12.830
This pond is nice,

08:12.830 --> 08:14.830
yet no fish can be caught here.

08:15.160 --> 08:17.560
Yes. I am

08:17.920 --> 08:19.380
like the fish in this pond.

08:20.830 --> 08:23.750
I look quite free when I'm inside,

08:24.480 --> 08:26.360
but it's not so easy to get out.

08:27.830 --> 08:30.240
I really miss the time we spent

08:30.360 --> 08:31.920
in the manor as children.

08:33.630 --> 08:35.240
I always dream about it.

08:36.960 --> 08:38.120
To be honest, Your Majesty,

08:38.120 --> 08:40.549
I actually dream about it often too.

08:41.630 --> 08:42.440
Oh, right.

08:42.549 --> 08:44.510
Recently I've moved
into the Xiao residence

08:44.510 --> 08:45.710
to live with Xiao Chi.

08:46.750 --> 08:48.870
So that means I'm the only one here?

08:50.080 --> 08:51.870
Seems so.

08:53.910 --> 08:54.630
Got one!

08:55.960 --> 08:56.720
Wow!

08:57.440 --> 08:58.670
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

08:58.670 --> 09:01.550
I will have a few drinks
with Xiao Chi tonight

09:01.550 --> 09:03.480
to celebrate your lucky catch.

09:04.270 --> 09:06.670
Maybe I should find a way these days

09:06.910 --> 09:08.630
to sneak out of the palace

09:08.630 --> 09:09.890
and come to your place.

09:09.960 --> 09:11.600
I'll sneak back

09:11.600 --> 09:13.060
before the morning court.

09:13.360 --> 09:14.490
Is that really okay?

09:14.720 --> 09:16.050
What's wrong with that?

09:16.120 --> 09:16.920
It's settled.

09:17.320 --> 09:20.240
Then, I obey your command.

09:21.320 --> 09:22.720
Let's catch another one.

09:22.870 --> 09:24.510
Since we're looking for good wine,

09:24.510 --> 09:26.750
I believe Ms. Tang must have some here.

09:27.120 --> 09:29.150
Xiao Chi, you're finally here.

09:29.150 --> 09:31.030
Good wine always reminds me of you.

09:31.030 --> 09:32.600
Then you've come to the right place.

09:32.600 --> 09:33.120
Please.

09:37.630 --> 09:40.510
The finest wine
from Tianlang Pass is here.

09:40.510 --> 09:41.910
This is...

09:42.720 --> 09:44.630
This is my father.

09:44.910 --> 09:46.240
I'm also the owner here.

09:47.150 --> 09:48.630
You are indeed capable.

09:48.630 --> 09:50.320
You've already
brought in guests so quickly.

09:50.320 --> 09:52.480
They're friends who came to support us.

09:52.480 --> 09:54.480
This is Xiao Chi.

09:54.480 --> 09:55.510
General Xiao?

09:55.510 --> 09:56.960
Aren't you meant to
be guarding Tianlang Pass?

09:56.960 --> 09:58.620
Why are you in the capital too?

09:59.240 --> 10:01.270
If he didn't come,
I wouldn't have come either.

10:01.270 --> 10:02.390
Pour the wine.

10:02.390 --> 10:03.360
Okay.

10:06.960 --> 10:07.750
Thank you.

10:18.960 --> 10:19.790
How is it?

10:19.960 --> 10:22.080
This wine is indeed good,

10:22.480 --> 10:23.940
but still not quite there.

10:24.360 --> 10:26.360
Is this the finest wine we have here?

10:26.440 --> 10:27.840
Yes, definitely.

10:28.600 --> 10:29.200
It's fine.

10:29.240 --> 10:30.960
Ms. Tang, we will

10:30.960 --> 10:32.000
try other places in the capital.

10:32.000 --> 10:32.480
Wait.

10:34.910 --> 10:36.150
Hurry

10:36.870 --> 10:40.480
and bring us another jar of our best wine.

10:40.750 --> 10:42.320
Good wine?

10:43.080 --> 10:44.870
I do have one,

10:44.910 --> 10:46.550
but the price…

10:46.550 --> 10:47.870
it's priceless.

10:47.870 --> 10:49.240
Forget the price.

10:49.240 --> 10:50.240
Just bring it out.

10:51.150 --> 10:52.630
Hurry up.

10:52.960 --> 10:54.510
Alright, okay.

11:01.720 --> 11:03.000
He really is my father.

11:03.870 --> 11:04.910
Really.

11:06.720 --> 11:07.510
Well.

11:08.030 --> 11:10.030
This is top-quality Nverhong wine.

11:10.080 --> 11:12.270
I sealed it myself when you were born.

11:12.320 --> 11:13.750
I was planning to serve it to your groom

11:13.750 --> 11:14.840
on your wedding day.

11:14.840 --> 11:16.200
How come I've never heard

11:16.200 --> 11:17.550
that I even had it?

11:17.550 --> 11:18.910
Isn't Nverhong wine

11:18.910 --> 11:20.630
supposed to be buried
underground for years?

11:20.630 --> 11:21.960
You know quite a bit.

11:22.030 --> 11:25.030
I've carried it with me
all over the country for so many years.

11:25.030 --> 11:27.360
Wherever I went, I buried it in the soil.

11:27.360 --> 11:28.080
This wine

11:28.080 --> 11:29.030
has absorbed

11:29.030 --> 11:30.840
the essence of sun and moon
from all over Jinglan.

11:30.840 --> 11:32.240
I was even saving it for your husband

11:32.240 --> 11:33.630
on your wedding day.

11:33.720 --> 11:36.080
Who cares about all that?

11:36.320 --> 11:37.450
Don't listen to him.

11:37.550 --> 11:38.720
If you want to drink,

11:38.720 --> 11:39.840
just drink.

11:40.910 --> 11:41.510
Forget it.

11:41.510 --> 11:43.550
We really can't accept
such a generous gift.

11:43.550 --> 11:44.440
Besides,

11:44.440 --> 11:45.600
this wine is also a gift for someone.

11:45.600 --> 11:46.480
So what?

11:46.840 --> 11:49.440
Whoever it is that
made you go to such lengths

11:49.440 --> 11:50.770
must be extraordinary.

11:51.480 --> 11:53.320
If you really feel bad about it,

11:53.440 --> 11:55.750
I can deliver the wine for you.

11:56.440 --> 11:57.240
Well.

12:02.510 --> 12:04.510
Thank you, Ms. Tang.

12:16.480 --> 12:18.720
This place is quite unique.

12:19.360 --> 12:21.560
What kind of person are we going to meet?

12:21.870 --> 12:22.720
He's…

12:22.910 --> 12:24.030
a strange man.

12:24.030 --> 12:24.960
a strange man?

12:27.120 --> 12:28.360
Interesting.

12:49.360 --> 12:50.480
Good wine.

12:50.480 --> 12:52.120
Shiba, do you smell that?

12:55.030 --> 12:55.750
Where is the good wine?

12:55.750 --> 12:56.600
Where is it?

12:56.600 --> 12:57.360
Right here.

12:59.320 --> 13:00.150
Who are you?

13:00.960 --> 13:01.890
Doesn't matter.

13:02.270 --> 13:03.840
This wine is for me, right?

13:04.360 --> 13:05.550
Your brother's been well taken care of.

13:05.550 --> 13:07.010
Go in and see for yourself.

13:10.550 --> 13:12.510
You're something else—

13:12.510 --> 13:14.170
you even found such fine wine.

13:14.440 --> 13:15.370
Let me have a sip.

13:16.550 --> 13:18.150
Why are you so rude?

13:18.150 --> 13:20.270
I've brought the wine for you.

13:20.270 --> 13:21.510
Whether you get to drink it or not

13:21.510 --> 13:23.080
depends on your own ability.

13:23.080 --> 13:23.540
This...

13:26.510 --> 13:27.170
Ah, this...

13:27.960 --> 13:30.160
Tell me—how can I get to drink this wine?

13:31.630 --> 13:32.480
Alright then.

13:33.030 --> 13:35.360
If you can guess my age,

13:35.630 --> 13:37.910
this wine is yours.

13:37.910 --> 13:39.670
Why don't you just tell me?

13:40.120 --> 13:41.180
Not going to guess?

13:41.550 --> 13:43.840
Looks like you won't get to taste it then.

13:46.910 --> 13:48.630
You are twenty-four.

13:49.910 --> 13:50.840
How did you know?

13:50.870 --> 13:51.720
Curious?

13:52.000 --> 13:52.480
Yeah.

13:55.840 --> 13:56.630
Here.

14:02.270 --> 14:03.440
You can tell me now.

14:06.910 --> 14:09.320
In Jinglan, if a woman
isn't married by eighteen,

14:09.320 --> 14:10.550
she wears a hairpin.

14:11.150 --> 14:12.360
Each year, she wears
a different colored hairpin—

14:12.360 --> 14:13.960
red, orange, yellow,
green, blue, indigo, violet.

14:13.960 --> 14:15.890
Today you're wearing a violet one,

14:15.960 --> 14:17.550
so you must be twenty-four.

14:17.870 --> 14:18.960
Already twenty-four and still not married.

14:18.960 --> 14:19.480
You...

14:19.960 --> 14:21.360
Don't tell me she's planning to marry you?

14:21.360 --> 14:22.080
Let me tell you,

14:22.080 --> 14:23.120
the girl inside is a good one.

14:23.120 --> 14:24.380
Don't disappoint her.

14:24.510 --> 14:26.440
Liu Xiyang, just drink your wine.

14:29.510 --> 14:30.960
Little puppy,

14:31.150 --> 14:32.510
you are so cute.

14:32.600 --> 14:33.670
What's your name?

14:34.150 --> 14:36.550
Shiba, why aren't you biting the stranger?

14:38.320 --> 14:39.480
Your name is Shiba?

14:39.720 --> 14:41.120
You won't bite me, right?

14:44.360 --> 14:46.750
Since you helped Xiao Chi,

14:46.960 --> 14:48.440
next time you come to my tavern,

14:48.440 --> 14:49.360
I'll treat you to drinks.

14:49.360 --> 14:51.440
I never leave this mountain.

14:51.720 --> 14:53.380
Just bring the good wine here.

14:55.550 --> 14:57.410
There's only one jar of this wine.

14:58.120 --> 14:58.910
Why?

14:59.240 --> 15:00.440
This is Nverhong wine,

15:00.440 --> 15:01.720
brewed by her father

15:01.720 --> 15:03.270
when she was born.

15:03.270 --> 15:05.080
It was saved for her future husband.

15:05.080 --> 15:06.600
If you want to drink it,

15:06.600 --> 15:07.800
go talk to her father.

15:14.120 --> 15:15.150
Nver...

15:16.360 --> 15:17.150
Nverhong wine?

15:17.150 --> 15:17.840
Yes.

15:21.360 --> 15:22.120
Future...

15:23.510 --> 15:24.360
husband?

15:31.240 --> 15:32.840
When are we getting married?

15:33.120 --> 15:35.120
Who said I'm going to marry you?

15:35.120 --> 15:36.510
Good then.

15:46.550 --> 15:47.630
I have to admit,

15:47.630 --> 15:49.490
those two are quite well matched.

15:49.750 --> 15:50.910
Yes, they are.

15:51.440 --> 15:52.120
I guess

15:52.120 --> 15:53.030
Tang Zhaoxue

15:53.030 --> 15:54.080
will now put all her attention

15:54.080 --> 15:55.270
on Liu Xiyang.

15:56.120 --> 15:57.750
Then you'll have it easy.

15:58.440 --> 15:59.240
Yeah.

16:00.150 --> 16:02.680
But Mo's case still needs
to be investigated.

16:02.840 --> 16:04.720
I'll review the files
with Chengfeng later.

16:04.720 --> 16:06.360
I also have matters to attend to.

16:06.360 --> 16:07.490
Then let's split up.

16:08.360 --> 16:10.150
Be careful on your own.

16:10.750 --> 16:11.960
Don't worry.

16:11.960 --> 16:13.670
I'll be home before sunset.

16:30.750 --> 16:31.630
Jin Xi.

16:33.150 --> 16:35.120
We've been here for so many days.

16:35.840 --> 16:38.550
When will the marriage ceremony
actually take place?

16:38.550 --> 16:39.880
Don't worry, Princess.

16:40.120 --> 16:41.480
Lord Fei

16:41.480 --> 16:43.940
has already gone
to the palace to see Liu Chu.

16:45.120 --> 16:46.440
I'm not in a hurry.

16:47.080 --> 16:48.120
I just want to...

16:50.550 --> 16:51.960
You want to see Liu Chu?

16:53.960 --> 16:55.030
No, I don't.

16:55.360 --> 16:56.510
I just want to see

16:56.510 --> 16:57.970
whether he's worthy of me.

16:59.240 --> 17:00.000
Chengfeng.

17:00.440 --> 17:01.000
General.

17:02.480 --> 17:03.550
How is the princess?

17:03.550 --> 17:04.440
She hasn't skipped a meal—

17:04.440 --> 17:06.369
she's been eating well every time.

17:06.680 --> 17:07.510
Has anyone come in?

17:07.510 --> 17:08.349
No, General.

17:08.349 --> 17:09.480
We're watching closely—

17:09.480 --> 17:10.880
no fly could get through.

17:12.960 --> 17:13.829
Come with me.

17:14.000 --> 17:14.510
Yes.

17:15.349 --> 17:16.829
Keep a close eye on her.

17:17.160 --> 17:17.640
Yes.

17:24.069 --> 17:25.200
Is everything here?

17:25.920 --> 17:28.200
All case files from
the past twenty years in the capital

17:28.200 --> 17:28.960
are here.

17:29.960 --> 17:32.880
Then where are the Han family's files
from over ten years ago?

17:32.880 --> 17:34.510
I don't know.

17:34.510 --> 17:35.710
I just guard the door.

17:35.750 --> 17:37.030
I'm not even qualified to read them.

17:37.030 --> 17:38.750
Even if I were allowed to see them,

17:38.750 --> 17:39.750
I wouldn't understand them anyway.

17:39.750 --> 17:41.310
You don't need to know them.

17:42.110 --> 17:43.570
Just keep your mouth shut.

17:43.920 --> 17:44.920
Don't worry, Lieutenant Xu.

17:44.920 --> 17:46.350
I don't even talk in my sleep.

17:46.350 --> 17:47.160
You can leave.

17:47.680 --> 17:48.480
Okay.

17:51.480 --> 17:53.750
General, there are so many files here.

17:54.070 --> 17:55.640
How long will it take to find it?

17:55.640 --> 17:58.270
Aren't you full of energy after eating?

17:58.270 --> 18:00.670
Then search properly.
If you can't find it,

18:00.830 --> 18:01.640
you won't get to eat.

18:01.640 --> 18:02.480
Wait, this...

18:04.480 --> 18:06.350
Fine, I'll search. I don't believe

18:06.350 --> 18:07.810
I can't find a single file.

18:47.550 --> 18:48.810
Sir, I need some herbs.

18:52.310 --> 18:53.440
Two qian of Zhiyuan.

18:54.310 --> 18:55.110
Okay.

18:56.350 --> 18:57.810
Five qian of Xingnantian.

18:58.830 --> 18:59.640
Okay.

19:23.720 --> 19:24.510
Thank you.

20:04.510 --> 20:05.640
Well.

20:06.720 --> 20:08.160
It's my first time

20:08.680 --> 20:11.160
sneaking out of the palace at night.

20:12.510 --> 20:14.440
This is so exciting—it's fun.

20:16.160 --> 20:17.310
Chu.

20:17.720 --> 20:19.720
Do you still remember that courtyard?

20:19.720 --> 20:21.270
The one Xiao Chi is living in now—

20:21.270 --> 20:23.400
do you remember who used to live there?

20:23.680 --> 20:24.550
Of course I do.

20:25.110 --> 20:26.110
My sister.

20:27.480 --> 20:30.510
I remember I was the only one
who dared to come and go freely.

20:30.510 --> 20:31.720
Whenever I went there,

20:31.720 --> 20:35.120
my sister would always prepare
lots of delicious food for me.

20:35.960 --> 20:38.480
Ah… those were such happy days.

20:38.720 --> 20:40.450
Do you want to go and take a look?

20:43.750 --> 20:44.640
Let's go.

20:45.480 --> 20:46.010
Let's go.

20:46.720 --> 20:47.880
Hey, be careful.

20:49.240 --> 20:51.720
It's so late, and you're not sleeping.

20:51.720 --> 20:53.680
Dragging me out to sit in this courtyard—

20:53.680 --> 20:55.310
what exactly do you want?

20:58.350 --> 20:59.160
Princess.

20:59.830 --> 21:01.880
Tonight is the full moon—

21:01.920 --> 21:03.270
a very auspicious night.

21:03.270 --> 21:05.270
I've heard that any wish

21:05.270 --> 21:07.030
made tonight can come true.

21:07.640 --> 21:08.310
Really?

21:08.750 --> 21:09.720
Of course.

21:09.720 --> 21:11.250
When have I ever lied to you?

21:12.160 --> 21:13.030
Then I'll try it.

21:13.030 --> 21:13.510
Okay.

21:18.160 --> 21:19.350
May...

21:20.070 --> 21:23.160
May I and the Emperor
of Jinglan be married soon,

21:23.750 --> 21:25.610
and grow old together in harmony.

21:37.110 --> 21:37.920
Ouch!

21:46.920 --> 21:48.440
That hurts!

21:51.750 --> 21:52.750
Who are you?

21:54.030 --> 21:55.160
You don't know me?

21:56.240 --> 21:57.680
No, I don't.

21:57.880 --> 21:58.240
I...

22:01.070 --> 22:03.830
I'm General Xiao's elder brother.

22:04.200 --> 22:04.920
And you?

22:06.750 --> 22:07.920
I'm from Changmo.

22:08.030 --> 22:09.290
My name is Jiang Wanyu.

22:09.480 --> 22:11.270
You're the princess

22:11.270 --> 22:13.510
from Changmo who came
for the marriage alliance, right?

22:13.510 --> 22:14.350
Yeah.

22:17.440 --> 22:18.350
Well,

22:18.680 --> 22:20.750
why did you fall from up there?

22:24.880 --> 22:25.920
I...

22:27.680 --> 22:29.160
I was up there getting some fresh air.

22:29.160 --> 22:30.090
It's quite cool.

22:30.510 --> 22:31.370
What about you?

22:32.480 --> 22:35.610
My female official told me that
tonight is the full moon.

22:35.680 --> 22:38.070
If you drink wine
and make a wish to the moon,

22:38.070 --> 22:39.070
it will come true.

22:39.920 --> 22:42.480
What did you wish for?

22:42.480 --> 22:44.350
Your fall made me forget my wish.

22:48.350 --> 22:49.350
But,

22:50.310 --> 22:51.200
sir,

22:51.440 --> 22:52.960
that must've hurt, right?

22:53.440 --> 22:54.880
A sip of wine will ease the pain.

22:54.880 --> 22:56.080
I'll pass on the wine.

22:56.480 --> 22:57.000
I have things to do.

22:57.000 --> 22:58.060
I should get going.

22:58.480 --> 22:59.480
What's your name?

22:59.550 --> 23:00.350
Chu!

23:00.830 --> 23:01.760
Are you alright?

23:02.240 --> 23:03.030
Lord Fei.

23:04.960 --> 23:06.490
Princess, you are here too.

23:08.110 --> 23:08.720
Princess,

23:08.920 --> 23:10.000
allow me to introduce him.

23:10.000 --> 23:10.480
This is...

23:10.480 --> 23:11.160
Well,

23:11.160 --> 23:12.890
I'll tell you who I am next time.

23:13.350 --> 23:14.310
This is too awkward.

23:14.310 --> 23:15.350
Get me out of here.

23:16.480 --> 23:16.920
Chu.

23:17.920 --> 23:18.350
This...

23:18.350 --> 23:19.160
this way.

23:21.310 --> 23:23.110
Princess, we'll take our leave.

23:25.960 --> 23:27.620
This is Mo's medicinal pouch,

23:29.750 --> 23:31.480
Xiao Chi's hangover medicine,

23:32.310 --> 23:34.640
and the silver needles for his treatment.

23:41.920 --> 23:43.270
It's almost dawn.

23:43.440 --> 23:44.970
Why hasn't he come back yet?

25:09.790 --> 25:11.110
Why are you just getting back?

25:11.110 --> 25:12.240
I...

25:13.240 --> 25:14.840
I was busy all day yesterday.

25:16.350 --> 25:17.350
Go to sleep first.

25:17.510 --> 25:18.570
I'll head back now.

25:19.160 --> 25:19.720
Wait.

25:22.720 --> 25:24.270
I didn't treat you yesterday.

25:24.270 --> 25:26.440
The silver needles
have been prepared overnight.

25:26.440 --> 25:28.440
Now is the best time for acupuncture.

25:28.440 --> 25:29.270
Now?

25:29.590 --> 25:30.070
Yes.
